            專業英文翻譯問題(營養方面)
        


1.Marasmus is calorie malnutrition and is evidenced by physical wasting of energy stores, including somatic protein and fat.
2.In clinical practice, it occurs when metabolic stress is placed on a chronically-starved individual. 
3.Malnutrition can be classified by loss of body weight, although one must consider...
 顯示更多 
 1.Marasmus is calorie malnutrition and is evidenced by physical wasting of energy stores, including somatic protein and fat. 
2.In clinical practice, it occurs when metabolic stress is placed on a chronically-starved individual.  
3.Malnutrition can be classified by loss of body weight, although one must consider the hydration status of the individual before doing so. 


這是三句話 我需要專業的翻譯~~~謝謝 

不要直接 軟體翻譯 謝謝





 
追蹤 


 
 1 個解答 
1


檢舉不當使用









您確定要刪除此解答嗎？
是
否












 









抱歉，似乎發生一些問題。



Trending Now





 

解答














最佳解答: 
             你好，很高興為你解答： 
1.消瘦是卡路里營養失調和顯示藉由身體能量貯存的浪費所造成的,包括謂蛋白和脂肪。 
2.在臨床的實習, 當這出現新陳代謝的重要性是放置在長期地-挨餓的個體上。  
3.營養失調可被分類在體重的流失, 然而必須認同在這個體水合作用做法之前。 




